<%- include("partials/header") %>

<main>
  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  <p><strong><%= openHours %></strong></p>

  <div class="faq-section">
    <h2><span role="img" aria-label="ticket">🎟️</span> Do I need to book tickets?</h2>
    <p>No – this site is just for promotion. Tickets aren’t sold online.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-section">
    <h2><span role="img" aria-label="family-friendly">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</span> Is the park family friendly?</h2>
    <p>Yes! There are attractions for all ages and abilities.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-section">
    <h2><span role="img" aria-label="food-and-drinks">🍔🍟</span> Are food and drinks available?</h2>
    <p>Yes – plenty of restaurants, cafes, and food trucks throughout the park.</p>
  </div>
</main>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>

<style>
  /* Use a custom Google font for a modern feel */
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap');

  main {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 3rem auto;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    border-radius: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    text-align: center;
    background-image: url('/img/faq-background.jpg'); /* Add your background image path here */
    background-size: cover;
    color: white;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; /* Apply custom font */
    background-position: center center;
  }

  h1 {
    color: #0077cc;
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .faq-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 20px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); /* Darker semi-transparent background for better text contrast */
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }

  .faq-section:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px); /* Slight lift effect on hover */
    box-shadow: 0px 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Increased shadow on hover */
  }

  .faq-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    color: #f0f0f0;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .faq-section p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .faq-section h2 span {
    font-size: 2.2rem; /* Larger emojis for better visibility */
  }

  /* Responsive design for mobile screens */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    main {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .faq-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }

    .faq-section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
